{"tid":1238704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［非分化］G20希望獨派「暫緩」港獨議程","createTime":"2019-06-18T02:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:12:30.000Z","uid":166567,"like":159,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"15420f58c4cf3662e68657bb724b978328d480fa","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:13:51.000Z","msg":"希望港獨派暫時停一停，因為現在g20提港獨，有副作用<br />\n1. 現時非最大光譜<br />\n2. 畀口實中央，話係港獨人士策動，然後模糊焦點。呢樣大家應該好熟<br />\n3. 國際輿論混亂，唔係個個咁清楚香港咩狀況，減弱運動成功率<br />\n<br />\n反而如果今次運動成功，這種抗爭模式畀市民慢慢接受。長遠對獨立派也有好處<br />\n<br />\n另外，放返喺美國形勢，trump都唔係我地最忠實盟友，佢D政敵先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但牽涉在港美國公民佢都不得不講兩句<br />\n<br />\n講liberate同港獨已經一樣<br />\n我想叫大家唔好邊個杯邊個，大家都係香港人，而且呢場運動我相信前線嘅係呢派嘅勇者都唔少<br />\n<br />\n然而，為香港而家好、長遠好，希望獨派自己可以明白去「暫緩」一下<br />\n<br />\n因此，請將焦點放返喺<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">SAVE FREEDOM OF HONG KONG<br />\nSAVE HUMAN RIGHT OF HONG KONG</span><br />\n<br />\nps 唔好暫我老母"},{"pid":"0c6993f5468328dcbf24c8ef1fc73263ba8f1d1b","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0ef4e7493de3e40ce6b0137ef8819f1872bccc3","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f74824ad2f9c4bd97f3bc58631f55ac993ba120","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:18:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8642b024cd7a0ccdaec680f9e65e8ba27e207360","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d96f66010dc8d45440db3a285f538e63bd0888d","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46a9197f1978a631e6d9a11ecd3f1bf6e25906ab","tid":1238704,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p